    "Following the modeling approach outlined above, we focus on the key tasks in the chemistry domain: Molecule Description, Molecule design, Product Inference, Retro-synthesis Prediction, and Yield Prediction.",
    "We construct instruction tuning datasets based on existing chemical, drug, and medicine datasets using prompt templates, in order to train models capable of addressing these tasks.",
    "Retro-synthesis Prediction.",
    "Retro-synthesis Prediction is a crucial task for chemistry.",
    "It involves inferring possible reaction pathways and conditions by given product molecules, thereby reversepredicting the synthetic route to generate the product."
